# YanZhu_414join
Nice to meet you all. My name is Lu Yueyue, and I am currently studying at Beijing Institute of Printing, majoring in digital media technology. 

On various Internet platforms I usually call myself “YanZhu”，It translates from Chinese to salt pillar, which comes from the story of Lot, the holy man in the Bible, whose wife did not listen to God's advice, but still had a nostalgia for her hometown - the city of sin, Sodom, and was turned into a pillar of salt when she turned back. It reminds me not to dwell on the past. 

I was born in a remote small town in the south, lacking in quality education resources and enlightened parents. The only constants in my childhood were pressure and loneliness, which led to my constant struggle against constraints. I believe that my experience is not unique, as most Chinese children spend their entire lives trying to come to terms with their childhoods - a period that is both the best and worst time in one's life. Therefore, I think I value the spiritual growth in the process more than the ultimate achievement.

By joining 414 Lab, I hope to get a focused and active learning environment, so as to overcome my inertia, increase my proficiency by increasing the frequency of using tools and software, and have the opportunity to practice the course knowledge through group cooperation. In addition, I want to get the latest information in the forefront of the industry and try not to make myself cognitively disconnected from the industry.

I inserted a picture of my love at the bottom of the post. It was a picture of me with my girlfriend, and the time I spent with her was one of my few happy moments.

Schisandra (Assassin) Schisandra (Guard) Baibei (Fangshi) Mai Dong (Lord) Futeng (Langzhong)
Different classes have different buffs or losses in different environments, and the combat environment is divided into "four qi" of cold, hot, warm and cool
The occupational name corresponds to the five flavors of Chinese medicinal materials
Assassin (Shōshin): Deals physical damage to enemy characters by releasing dark weapons in the shadows, etc
Fangshi (White Shell): Deals spell damage to enemy characters by crafting potions, etc
Guard (Gomi): Blocks the damage inflicted by the enemy on the boss and rebounds a portion of the damage to the enemy boss
Lord (Mai Dong): The boss of this faction, mainly taking damage, unable to deal damage to enemies, and has special skills such as skipping enemy release skill sessions
Lang Zhong (Kazeto): Each time a skill is released, it restores part of the health of the character in the faction, and restores the energy required for the character in the faction to release the skill

Assassin (Xiaoxin) Professional Background: The Assassin had a happy family when he was a child, and although he was an ordinary people, he lived a good and indisputable life, but the enemy country invaded, and the place he passed was full of smoke and grass. In the midst of the war, Ta witnessed the scene of his parents and villagers being brutally killed by the enemy, and he escaped because he hid in the closet, and he wanted to avenge his parents without power, and he was still young and his strength was too weak, so he learned the skills of assassins, trying to use the cold gun to eliminate the enemy and avenge his family and villagers. Because of his talent and the grief of the death of his loved ones, Ta worked hard to learn the technique, regardless of the cold winter and heat, he was bent on revenge, and injuries were only used as child's play, and there were often cases such as abrasions and bone cracks, but Ta never gave up and continued to improve his sneak attack skills. Ta quickly grasped the essence of the Assassin and became a proud protégé of the Hermit Assassin, growing up to be able to kill people invisibly without leaving a trace. The basic technique that Ta learned at the beginning was to "flick his fingers between his sleeves", slightly raise his arm and eject a few willow leaves to cause instant damage to the enemy; In addition, "smart needles are like mustard", multiple silver needles pop out of the fingertips, which can cause instantaneous damage to the enemy's key points while breaking the shield and making the enemy enter a weak state; The third move is "Ice Blade Drinking Blood and Wearing Flowers", which releases multiple darts in the shadows and deals continuous damage to enemies for three seconds; The unique move is "10,000 arrows through the body without return", throwing out multiple quenched cold arrows, which can deal maximum instantaneous damage and five seconds of continuous damage to enemies.
